article.title: 'Kusuriya no Hitorigoto' 3rd Season Airs in Split Cours, Gets Original Movie in December 2026
article.summary: The official website for the television anime adaptation of Natsu Hyuuga's Kusuriya no Hitorigoto (The Apothecary Diaries) light novel announced an original anime movie on Wednesday. The movie, featuring a completely new story by Hyuuga, is scheduled to premiere in December 2026. Norihiro Naganuma (Mahoutsukai no Yome) is returning to direct the movie.
